headline: ITB: A Guide To Understanding This Homebuilders ETF
summary: ITB offers exposure to U.S. homebuilders, mostly mid-caps, with a value tilt but significant volatility. Read more on why ITB is for long-term, risk-tolerant investors.

headline: New homes take root at Turnleaf with Builder lineup, model reveal
summary: GreenPointe Holdings proudly announces sales are underway at Turnleaf, a new master-planned destination located just minutes from the expansive beaches of Florida's Gulf Coast. Turnleaf's premier builder lineup features three of the region's most respected homebuilders: Dream Finders Homes, Lennar and Perry Homes.
